ZH: 这场灾害给我们的家园带来了严重的破坏。
EN: This disaster brought serious damage to our homeland.

ZH: 雨水过多导致了山体滑坡，引发了一场灾难。
EN: Excessive rainfall caused a landslide, triggering a disaster.

ZH: 这起火灾造成了数十人受伤。
EN: This fire disaster caused dozens of people to be injured.

ZH: 牛群被暴风雪困在了高山之上，面临饥饿和灾难的威胁。
EN: The herd of cows was trapped on the top of the mountain due to a snowstorm, facing the threat of hunger and disaster.

ZH: 沙漠化是地球上的一场无法避免的环境灾难。
EN: Desertification is an unavoidable environmental disaster on Earth.

